data.description: Fantastic family home in North Lakeport!  2bd/2ba home has been a much loved vacation get a way for sellers family for decades!  Expansive living areas,  covered wrap around deck, garden tub and extra deep covered carport are only a few of it's charms.  Lakeview, beach rights, and boating and fishing at private beach area across the street from Walnut Dr. make this an amazing place to live!  Easy care landscaping includes two lemon trees and a lowquat tree surrounded by rock landscaping.  Two storage sheds on the property, storage areas beneath the deck and more.
